India Direct Tax Collections Rise 6.6%, Official Says

-- B y   A n t o   A n t o n y
-- 
2011-09-21T10:32:57Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-21/india-direct-tax-collections-rise-6-6-official-says-correct-.html
(Corrects to add percentage symbol in headline.)  India ’s direct tax collections rose
6.6 percent to 1.8 trillion rupees as of Sept. 15, a finance
ministry official told reporters in  New Delhi  today on condition
of anonymity.  Advance taxes paid by the nation’s top 100 companies in the
first half of the year ending March rose 12 percent, according
to a statement issued by the ministry.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Anto Antony in New Delhi at 
